title: Hale Dwoskin - Breakthroughs in Consciousness Sedona Method MP3
description:
This four-recording set by Hale will accelerate your releasing and catapult you deeper into the core of your Being. Breakthroughs in Consciousness begins by exploring welcoming, which is a natural part of your beingness. It is the state of existence that opens you up and helps you in the releasing process. Hale then leads you through exploring concepts directly.

One of the main barriers to exploring the freedom that is here and now are the concepts we hold in mind. By choosing to let them go, we start to discover the underlying unity, underlying stillness, the underlying truth, and that which is beyond all concepts. Recording #3 contains a process for welcoming your day; and Recording #4 has a release to allow you to fully let go before going to sleep at night.

Course Contents

Audio Set 1: Welcome
Audio Set 2: Beyond Concepts
Audio Set 3: Good Morning
Audio Set 4: Good Night

MP3 - 128 kbps - CBR
